## How to Use

1. Open `presentation.html` in any browser (double-click the file)
2. Navigate with **← →** arrow keys, click dots, or use the **‹ ›** buttons
3. Touch swipe is supported for tablets
4. Press **Home**/**End** to jump to first/last slide
